channel.title: DaggerFall 377 by adrian & Mursa
channel.description:
DaggerFall 377 is a project Czar based source, but we deleted everything and restarted almost from scratch, but with class files and stuff. so yea, running and walking is made by us.
[size=24pt]About DaggerFall[/size] DaggerFall is a 377 server which is made by adrian1372 and Mursa. I closed my server and he closed his server cause we hoped to get more players if we worked together. We have almost no customs, as the server is being ruined with them. There are always some wire problems in customs which makes you invinsible. So we are trying to keep the server as clean of customs as possible. DaggerFall is a pretty clean server at the moment. I have released the client for beta testing. It is in hamachi and I might add the hamachi information at the website. The link for website can be found in my signature. If u wanna beta test... You have to find the dl link at the daggerfall forums. Should be pretty easy. But: When u join the hamachi channel and try to login with wor.almenningen.org... you will get error. You have to click enter twice to get down to the ip... and replace it with the ip the computer in hamachi channel called adrian has... But enuf said about beta testing. We are just getting started... WE are making one soon. I hope you will come with positive comments :D We have now made a ::player command which shows all players online. And for the days we have loads of them... I'be added a player counter at the top of the interface that pops up. We also have a high-level trainng area now.
[size=24pt]Supporters and the team[/size] for you mods: If i am not supposed to post this here, please tell me and i will remove it. TEAM Lead Developers: Adrian Mursa Server Developers Adrian npc spawn makers (includes npc drops): none Client developer mursa Adrian Also thanks to: YoudripredRSPS for uploading pics to photobucket

No teleports… WTF
Where do i train when i’m highlevel? …
How am i supposed to get money?[/quote]

I said: Almost clean server and we are at V0.1A -.-
Do you think we have all the features nessecary yet? NO
Do you think I care if u hate it as it is now? NO cause it will be better
Teleports will be made. Until that time… Live with only one area…
High-level train area will be made when low-level is finished! Be patient…

Update:
We now have a high-level area. It’s crowded by npc’s, i know! Don’t complain
